	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName> <date>Tamuz 8th 5614</date> AM.</p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>July 4th</date></p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Revd. Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee> <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#33;</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">Dear Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Enclosed you will find two dollars for the Occi&#45;<lb/>dent&#59; but strange I did not receive one No. since <date>Oct.</date><lb/> last and No. <hi rend="underline"><date><sic>Novembre</sic> 1853</date> <date>Jan. 1854</date> <date>Feb.</date> <date>Mrch</date> <date>Apr.</date> <date>May</date>&#44; <date>June</date> &#38; <date>July</date></hi><lb/> I miss&#59; consequently am short of these Nos. in order to make<lb/> the volume complete&#59; as I file them&#59; since I am a sub&#44;<lb/>scriber.  Please forward them to me to my annexed re&#45;<lb/>siding place&#59; but it is time enough&#44; if you send them&#44; when<lb/> the next No. is issued.  You will oblige me also by in&#45;<lb/>serting my marriage Notice in your next No. &#40;which is enclosed&#41;<lb/> and <sic>chrge</sic> the same to my a&#47;c.  With the compliance of<lb/> these requests&#44; I shall feel under many obligations</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">to you  Yours Resp.</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">Solomon Weil</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><placeName>No. 469 Eight Avenue</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><placeName>between 34th &#38; 35th Str.</placeName></p>
				<p>P. S. If you deem it proper&#8212;I have visit the place &#38; got all these<lb/> informations&#44; from the Sect. <persName>Mr. Cohen</persName>&#8212;who is my Bro. in Law&#8212;to insert<lb/> the enclosed in your valuable Periodical&#44; resp. <placeName>Newark N. J.</placeName> it shall be to your disposition.</p>
		</body>
